#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.27:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Uruvelavagga "
msgstr "3. At Uruvelā "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Santuṭṭhisutta "
msgstr "27. Contentment "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.27, sc1
#. VAR: ca → ceva (mr)
msgctxt "an4.27:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, appāni ca sulabhāni ca, tāni ca anavajjāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four trifles are easy to get hold of and are blameless. "

msgctxt "an4.27:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.27:1.3"
msgid "Paṃsukūlaṃ, bhikkhave, cīvarānaṃ appañca sulabhañca, tañca anavajjaṃ. "
msgstr "Rag-robes … "

msgctxt "an4.27:1.4"
msgid "Piṇḍiyālopo, bhikkhave, bhojanānaṃ appañca sulabhañca, tañca anavajjaṃ. "
msgstr "A lump of alms-food … "

msgctxt "an4.27:1.5"
msgid "Rukkhamūlaṃ, bhikkhave, senāsanānaṃ appañca sulabhañca, tañca anavajjaṃ. "
msgstr "Lodgings at the root of a tree … "

msgctxt "an4.27:1.6"
msgid "Pūtimuttaṃ, bhikkhave, bhesajjānaṃ appañca sulabhañca, tañca anavajjaṃ. "
msgstr "Fermented urine as medicine … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.27:1.7"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri appāni ca sulabhāni ca, tāni ca anavajjāni. "
msgstr "These four trifles are easy to get hold of and are blameless. "

#. VAR: sāmaññaṅganti → sāmaññanti (mr)
msgctxt "an4.27:1.8"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appena ca tuṭṭho hoti sulabhena ca, idamassāhaṃ aññataraṃ sāmaññaṅganti vadāmīti. "
msgstr "When a mendicant is content with trifles that are easy to get hold of, they have one of the factors of the ascetic life, I say. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.27:2.1"
msgid "Anavajjena tuṭṭhassa, "
msgstr "When you’re content with what’s blameless, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.2"
msgid "appena sulabhena ca; "
msgstr "trifling, and easy to get hold of, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.3"
msgid "Na senāsanamārabbha, "
msgstr "you don’t get upset "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.4"
msgid "cīvaraṃ pānabhojanaṃ; "
msgstr "about lodgings, robes, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.5"
msgid "Vighāto hoti cittassa, "
msgstr "food, and drink, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.6"
msgid "disā nappaṭihaññati. "
msgstr "and you’re not obstructed anywhere. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.27:3.1"
msgid "Ye cassa dhammā akkhātā, "
msgstr "These qualities are said to be "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:3.2"
msgid "sāmaññassānulomikā; "
msgstr "integral to the ascetic life. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:3.3"
msgid "Adhiggahitā tuṭṭhassa, "
msgstr "They’re acquired by one who trains, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:3.4"
msgid "appamattassa sikkhato”ti. "
msgstr "content and diligent.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.27:3.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
